installationInstructions.title: replace the ribbon cable for the water/ice dispenser
installationInstructions.content: I replaced the paddle for the water dispenser in the refrigerator and in that process the ribbon cable shorted out from the bending and the electricity did not go through so I ordered a new ribbon cable which was easy to install.
